{"tid":254840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"騙徒自稱乾隆皇帝吃了長生不老藥　深圳富婆被呃222萬人仔","createTime":"2017-05-23T13:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T13:08:48.000Z","uid":103608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da436c71adacb163d382809a4c236897fa0e842f","tid":254840,"uid":103608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"一名男子冒充「乾隆皇帝」在深圳行騙，聲稱「我是乾隆皇帝，吃了長生不老藥，活了300多歲，掌握着大清皇家的資產，不過這些資產被凍結了，需要找人投入啟動資金」，又指投資者可以獲得幾倍甚至幾十倍收益。這個瀰天大謊竟然也成功騙走深圳一名富婆200多萬元人民幣。涉案男子今日在深圳中級人民法院受審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《廣州日報》報道，之前曾有冒充公主、格格等皇室後裔詐騙的案子，但直接冒充皇帝本人的，卻是本案被告劉乾珍「首創」。自稱是長生不老的乾隆皇帝，一般人聽到這種謊言都會一笑置之，然而，深圳一名富婆卻被這名冒牌乾隆皇帝騙走200多萬元人民幣。而和「乾隆皇帝」拍檔詐騙的則是曾冒充金融大鱷索羅斯弟子的男子萬健民。<br />\n<br />\n案情顯示，劉乾珍謊稱自己是乾隆皇帝，吃了長生不老藥，活了300多歲，是全世界27個皇家家族之一，掌握大清皇家大量資產。萬健民也謊稱自己是萬氏家族第九代傳人，只有通過他才能將皇家的錢解凍出來。鄭姓被害人對此信以為真，被劉乾珍以運作皇家資金以及購買玉白菜為由騙取222萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n後來，鄭的丈夫有所懷疑，質疑被告「你說你活了幾百歲？這不科學啊」，鄭的丈夫其後把錄音交予偵查機關調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170522/s00004/1495434155780#sthash.S5ydkEyD.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170522%2Fs00004%2F1495434155780%23sthash.S5ydkEyD.dpuf&d=aWio27DJuOuyfsjc3mJj98VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3f1fa75f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170522%2Fs00004%2F1495434155780%23sthash.S5ydkEyD.dpuf&h=d63fe472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170522/s00004/1495434155780#sthash.S5ydkEyD.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"99de734ac9a1348cdfab8b3af944464f0f81bb14","tid":254840,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"咁都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221a785d6e06403b646270e4969dfb5c929b94a8","tid":254840,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做皇帝咁跟得上潮流，大清遺產要銀行解凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}